00:26:02,185 --> 00:26:03,895
This is the concept for hair. How is it?

472
00:26:03,979 --> 00:26:05,188
Don't doll up. Keep it natural.

473
00:26:05,272 --> 00:26:07,107
-Don't doll up. Keep it natural. Okay.
