481
00:26:19,577 --> 00:26:21,329
-Enough.
-Should we wrap it in plastic

482
00:26:21,413 --> 00:26:22,622
or paper?

483
00:26:23,999 --> 00:26:25,000
That's hard.

484
00:26:25,959 --> 00:26:27,127
Which wig should we use

485
00:26:27,210 --> 00:26:28,753
-for Sin-ae's disguise?
-The right one.

486
00:26:28,837 --> 00:26:30,797
Which design for the tattoo
on Gyeong-jae's back?

487
00:26:30,880 --> 00:26:34,551
He once planned to have a trendy one,
size of two fingers,

488
00:26:34,634 --> 00:26:36,386
but he got swayed by
the yakuza-style tattoo.

489
00:26:36,469 --> 00:26:38,722
Make it look like something in between.

490
00:26:40,181 --> 00:26:42,475
What shall I order for lunch?

491
00:26:42,976 --> 00:26:43,977
Anything you want.

492
00:26:45,270 --> 00:26:48,481
The director swears in Scene 33,
Episode 2.

493
00:26:48,565 --> 00:26:50,275
Will it be revised or bleeped out?

494
00:26:50,358 --> 00:26:52,986
-Bleeped.
-How much of it should be heard?

495
00:26:53,320 --> 00:26:56,448
You can tell it's obviously a swear word,
but it'll be vaguely bleeped,

496
00:26:56,531 --> 00:26:58,783
so it'll be hard
for the inspectors to tell.

497
00:26:58,867 --> 00:27:01,244
It'll be so vague that it will
make them think for 16 episodes

498
00:27:01,328 --> 00:27:04,247
whether they should give us
a warning or not.

499
00:27:05,582 --> 00:27:09,294
How many lanes will Dong-u run across
in Scene 6, Episode 3?

500
00:27:09,377 --> 00:27:10,378
Six lanes.

501
00:27:10,712 --> 00:27:12,464
It'll be hard to get permission for that.

502
00:27:12,547 --> 00:27:14,215
-Five lanes.
-That too.

