00:27:20,847 --> 00:27:23,224
The pretty flowers you mentioned earlier,

506
00:27:23,558 --> 00:27:25,769
what kind of flowers are pretty?

507
00:27:30,106 --> 00:27:33,610
When you say "enough",

508
00:27:33,902 --> 00:27:35,236
how many...

